sub_title: Docent Koreaans, Korean teacher for non-Korean speakers
summary:
안녕하세요!

After completing the state program for Korean language education in Seoul, I decided to move to The Netherlands to explore new cultures and challenges. 

I love meeting new people and believe that language exchange can connect us. I am passionate about sharing my knowledge and experiences as a Korean native speaker. 

My mission is to create a learning environment in which my students can develop Korean language abilities and gain knowledge about (modern) Korean culture. In other words, I aim to provide various learning activities that build confidence, are fun, and prepare students for real-life interaction in Korean.
